field="Is_Approved__c" fieldtargetobjects="genesis__Applications__c" value="false"/></renderconditions><enableconditions/><template><!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <script>
        var autocomplete26,
            accModelSMSFShipping = skuid.model.getModel('AccountBillingAddress'),
            accRowSMSFShipping = accModelSMSFShipping.data[0],
            autoCompleteInput26 = document.getElementById('CompanyCAddress');
            //Google Place Initialize
            function initAutocompleteTrustMailing() {
                autocomplete26 = new google.maps.places.Autocomplete(autoCompleteInput26, {types: ['geocode']});
               
                //Restrict the google place only show the specified country address and not allow other country address.
                autocomplete26.setComponentRestrictions({
                   country: ["aus"]
                });
                
                google.maps.event.addListener(autocomplete26, "place_changed", function() {
                  var place = autocomplete26.getPlace();
                  autoCompleteInput26.value = place.formatted_address;
                  if(place){
                    var formatted_address = place.formatted_address;
                    var placeComponent = place.address_components;
                    fillInAddress7(placeComponent,formatted_address);
                  }else{
                    alert('Address not found.Please check your address details.');
                  }
                });
            }
            
            //Address data fillup for each type.
            function fillInAddress7(placeComponent,formatted_address) {
              $.each(placeComponent,function(i,rowSMSFShipping){
                    if(rowSMSFShipping.types=='premise' || rowSMSFShipping.types=='route'){
                        var fullStreetName = rowSMSFShipping.long_name.split(" ");
                        var lengthFullStreetName = fullStreetName.length;
                        if(lengthFullStreetName == 2){
                            accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                            Street_Name__c : rowSMSFShipping.long_name.split(" ")[0]
                            });
                        }
                        else if(lengthFullStreetName > 2){
                            var streetName='';
                            for(var i=0;i<lengthFullStreetName-1;i++){
                                streetName = streetName + rowSMSFShipping.long_name.split(" ")[i]+' ';
                            }
                            accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                                Street_Name__c : streetName
                            });
                        }
                        accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                            Street_Type__c : rowSMSFShipping.long_name.split(" ")[lengthFullStreetName-1]
                        });
                        accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                            Duplicate_Street_Type__c : rowSMSFShipping.short_name.split(" ")[lengthFullStreetName-1]
                        });
                    }
                    else if(rowSMSFShipping.types.includes('sublocality_level_1')){
                        var fullStreetName = rowSMSFShipping.long_name.split(" ");
                        var lengthFullStreetName = fullStreetName.length;
                        if(lengthFullStreetName == 2){
                            accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                                Street_Name__c : rowSMSFShipping.long_name.split(" ")[0]
                            });
                        }
                        else if(lengthFullStreetName > 2){
                            var streetName='';
                            for(var i=0;i<lengthFullStreetName-1;i++){
                                streetName = streetName + rowSMSFShipping.long_name.split(" ")[i]+' ';
                            }
                            accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                                Street_Name__c : streetName
                            });
                        }
                        accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                            Street_Type__c : rowSMSFShipping.long_name.split(" ")[lengthFullStreetName-1]
                        });
                        accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                            Duplicate_Street_Type__c : rowSMSFShipping.short_name.split(" ")[lengthFullStreetName-1]
                        });
                    }
                    else if(rowSMSFShipping.types.includes('locality')){
                            accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                            clcommon__City__c : (rowSMSFShipping.long_name).toUpperCase()
                        });
                    }
                    else if(rowSMSFShipping.types.includes('administrative_area_level_1')){
                        accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                            State__c : rowSMSFShipping.short_name
                        });
                        accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                            Duplicate_State_Name__c : rowSMSFShipping.short_name
                        });
                    }
                    else if(rowSMSFShipping.types.includes('subpremise')){
                            accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                            clcommon__County__c : rowSMSFShipping.long_name
                        });
                    }
                    else if(rowSMSFShipping.types.includes('country')){ 
                           accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                            clcommon__Country__c : rowSMSFShipping.long_name
                        });
                    }
                    else if(rowSMSFShipping.types.includes('street_number')){
                        accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                            Street_No__c : rowSMSFShipping.long_name
                        });
                    }
                    else if(rowSMSFShipping.types.includes('postal_code')){
                            accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                            clcommon__Zip_Code__c : rowSMSFShipping.long_name
                        });
                    }
              }) ; 
            }

            //Get and Set the location.
            function geolocate() {
                if (navigator.geolocation) {
                    navigator.geolocation.getCurrentPosition(function(position) {
                      var geolocation = {
                        lat: position.coords.latitude,
                        lng: position.coords.longitude
                      };
                      var circle = new google.maps.Circle(
                          {center: geolocation, radius: position.coords.accuracy});
                      autocomplete26.setBounds(circle.getBounds());
                    });
                }
            }
            function keepCheckingForAutoComplete(){
                if(typeof google === "undefined"){
                    setTimeout(keepCheckingForAutoComplete, 1000);
                }
                else{
                    initAutocompleteTrustMailing();
                }
            }
            keepCheckingForAutoComplete();
            
        </script>
</head>

field="Is_Approved__c" fieldtargetobjects="genesis__Applications__c" value="false"/></renderconditions><enableconditions/><template><!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <script>
        var autocomplete5,
            accModelSMSFMailing = skuid.model.getModel('AccountShippingAddress'),
            accRowSMSFMailing = accModelSMSFMailing.data[0],
            autoCompleteInput5 = document.getElementById('CompanyRegisteredAddress');
            //Google Place Initialize
            function initAutocompleteRegisterAddress() {
                autocomplete5 = new google.maps.places.Autocomplete(autoCompleteInput5, {types: ['geocode']});
               
                //Restrict the google place only show the specified country address and not allow other country address.
                autocomplete5.setComponentRestrictions({
                   country: ["aus"]
                });
                
                google.maps.event.addListener(autocomplete5, "place_changed", function() {
                  var place = autocomplete5.getPlace();
                  autoCompleteInput5.value = place.formatted_address;
                  if(place){
                    var formatted_address = place.formatted_address;
                    var placeComponent = place.address_components;
                    fillInAddress(placeComponent,formatted_address);
                  }else{
                    alert('Address not found.Please check your address details.');
                  }
                });
            }
            
            //Address data fillup for each type.
            function fillInAddress(placeComponent,formatted_address) {
              $.each(placeComponent,function(i,rowSMSFMailing){
                    if(rowSMSFMailing.types=='premise' || rowSMSFMailing.types=='route'){
                        var fullStreetName = rowSMSFMailing.long_name.split(" ");
                        var lengthFullStreetName = fullStreetName.length;
                        if(lengthFullStreetName == 2){
                             accModelSMSFMailing.updateRow(accRowSMSFMailing,{
                                Street_Name__c : rowSMSFMailing.long_name.split(" ")[0]
                            });
                        }
                        else if(lengthFullStreetName > 2){
                            var streetName='';
                            for(var i=0;i<lengthFullStreetName-1;i++){
                                streetName = streetName + rowSMSFMailing.long_name.split(" ")[i]+' ';
                            }
                            accModelSMSFMailing.updateRow(accRowSMSFMailing,{
                                Street_Name__c : streetName
                            });
                        }
                        accModelSMSFMailing.updateRow(accRowSMSFMailing,{
                            Street_Type__c : rowSMSFMailing.long_name.split(" ")[lengthFullStreetName-1]
                        });
                        accModelSMSFMailing.updateRow(accRowSMSFMailing,{
                            Duplicate_Street_Type__c : rowSMSFMailing.short_name.split(" ")[lengthFullStreetName-1]
                        });
                    }
                    else if(rowSMSFMailing.types.includes('sublocality_level_1')){
                        var fullStreetName = rowSMSFMailing.long_name.split(" ");
                        var lengthFullStreetName = fullStreetName.length;
                        if(lengthFullStreetName == 2){
                            accModelSMSFMailing.updateRow(accRowSMSFMailing,{
                                Street_Name__c : rowSMSFMailing.long_name.split(" ")[0]
                            });
                        }
                        else if(lengthFullStreetName > 2){
                            var streetName='';
                            for(var i=0;i<lengthFullStreetName-1;i++){
                                streetName = streetName + rowSMSFMailing.long_name.split(" ")[i]+' ';
                            }
                            accModelSMSFMailing.updateRow(accRowSMSFMailing,{
                                Street_Name__c : streetName
                            });
                        }
                        accModelSMSFMailing.updateRow(accRowSMSFMailing,{
                            Street_Type__c : rowSMSFMailing.long_name.split(" ")[lengthFullStreetName-1]
                        });
                        accModelSMSFMailing.updateRow(accRowSMSFMailing,{
                            Duplicate_Street_Type__c : rowSMSFMailing.short_name.split(" ")[lengthFullStreetName-1]
                        });
                    }
                    else if(rowSMSFMailing.types.includes('locality')){
                        accModelSMSFMailing.updateRow(accRowSMSFMailing,{
                            clcommon__City__c : (rowSMSFMailing.long_name).toUpperCase()
                        });
                    }
                    else if(rowSMSFMailing.types.includes('administrative_area_level_1')){
                        accModelSMSFMailing.updateRow(accRowSMSFMailing,{
                            State__c : rowSMSFMailing.short_name
                        });
                        accModelSMSFMailing.updateRow(accRowSMSFMailing,{
                            Duplicate_State_Name__c : rowSMSFMailing.short_name
                        });
                    }
                    else if(rowSMSFMailing.types.includes('subpremise')){
                        accModelSMSFMailing.updateRow(accRowSMSFMailing,{
                            clcommon__County__c : rowSMSFMailing.long_name
                        });
                    }
                    else if(rowSMSFMailing.types.includes('country')){
                        //accRow.OtherCountry = row.long_name ;
                        accModelSMSFMailing.updateRow(accRowSMSFMailing,{
                            clcommon__Country__c : rowSMSFMailing.long_name
                        });
                    }
                    else if(rowSMSFMailing.types.includes('street_number')){
                        //accRow.OtherCountry = row.long_name ;
                        accModelSMSFMailing.updateRow(accRowSMSFMailing,{
                            Street_No__c : rowSMSFMailing.long_name
                        });
                    }
                    else if(rowSMSFMailing.types.includes('postal_code')){
                        //accRow.OtherPostalCode = row.long_name ;
                        accModelSMSFMailing.updateRow(accRowSMSFMailing,{
                            clcommon__Zip_Code__c : rowSMSFMailing.long_name
                        });
                    }

              }) ; 
            }

            //Get and Set the location.
            function geolocate() {
                if (navigator.geolocation) {
                    navigator.geolocation.getCurrentPosition(function(position) {
                      var geolocation = {
                        lat: position.coords.latitude,
                        lng: position.coords.longitude
                      };
                      var circle = new google.maps.Circle(
                          {center: geolocation, radius: position.coords.accuracy});
                      autocomplete5.setBounds(circle.getBounds());
                    });
                }
            }

            function keepCheckingForAutoComplete(){
                if(typeof google === "undefined"){
                    setTimeout(keepCheckingForAutoComplete, 1000);
                }
                else{
                    initAutocompleteRegisterAddress();
                }
            }
            keepCheckingForAutoComplete();
            
        </script>
</head>

<body>
    <div id="locationField">
        <input id="CompanyRegisteredAddress" placeholder="Enter your address" onFocus="geolocate()" type="text" />
    </div>
</body>

nosourcerowbehavior="deactivate" field="Is_Approved__c" fieldtargetobjects="genesis__Applications__c" value="false"/></renderconditions><enableconditions/><template><!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <script>
        var autocomplete7,
            accModel = skuid.model.getModel('AccountTradingAddress'),
            accRow = accModel.data[0],
            autoCompleteInput7 = document.getElementById('CompanyTAddress');
            //Google Place Initialize
            function initAutocompleteTrustTrading() {
                autocomplete7 = new google.maps.places.Autocomplete(autoCompleteInput7, {types: ['geocode']});
               
                //Restrict the google place only show the specified country address and not allow other country address.
                autocomplete7.setComponentRestrictions({
                   country: ["aus"]
                });
                
                google.maps.event.addListener(autocomplete7, "place_changed", function() {
                  var place = autocomplete7.getPlace();
                  autoCompleteInput7.value = place.formatted_address;
                  if(place){
                    var formatted_address = place.formatted_address;
                    var placeComponent = place.address_components;
                    fillInAddress20(placeComponent,formatted_address);
                  }else{
                    alert('Address not found.Please check your address details.');
                  }
                });
            }
            
            //Address data fillup for each type.
            function fillInAddress20(placeComponent,formatted_address) {
              $.each(placeComponent,function(i,row){ 
                    if(row.types=='premise' || row.types=='route'){
                        var fullStreetName = row.long_name.split(" ");
                        var lengthFullStreetName = fullStreetName.length;
                        if(lengthFullStreetName == 2){
                            accModel.updateRow(accRow,{
                                Street_Name__c : row.long_name.split(" ")[0]
                            });
                        }
                        else if(lengthFullStreetName > 2){
                            var streetName='';
                            for(var i=0;i<lengthFullStreetName-1;i++){
                                streetName = streetName + row.long_name.split(" ")[i]+' ';
                            }
                            accModel.updateRow(accRow,{
                                Street_Name__c : streetName
                            });
                        }
                        accModel.updateRow(accRow,{
                            Street_Type__c : row.long_name.split(" ")[lengthFullStreetName-1]
                        });
                        accModel.updateRow(accRow,{
                            Duplicate_Street_Type__c : row.short_name.split(" ")[lengthFullStreetName-1]
                        });
                    }
                    else if(row.types.includes('sublocality_level_1')){
                        var fullStreetName = row.long_name.split(" ");
                        var lengthFullStreetName = fullStreetName.length;
                        if(lengthFullStreetName == 2){
                            accModel.updateRow(accRow,{
                                Street_Name__c : row.long_name.split(" ")[0]
                            });
                        }
                        else if(lengthFullStreetName > 2){
                            var streetName='';
                            for(var i=0;i<lengthFullStreetName-1;i++){
                                streetName = streetName + row.long_name.split(" ")[i]+' ';
                            }
                            accModel.updateRow(accRow,{
                                Street_Name__c : streetName
                            });
                        }
                        accModel.updateRow(accRow,{
                            Street_Type__c : row.long_name.split(" ")[lengthFullStreetName-1]
                        });
                        accModel.updateRow(accRow,{
                            Duplicate_Street_Type__c : row.short_name.split(" ")[lengthFullStreetName-1]
                        });
                    }
                    else if(row.types.includes('locality')){
                        //accRow.OtherCity = row.long_name ;
                        accModel.updateRow(accRow,{
                            clcommon__City__c : (row.long_name).toUpperCase()
                        });
                    }
                    else if(row.types.includes('administrative_area_level_1')){
                        //accRow.OtherState = row.long_name ;
                        accModel.updateRow(accRow,{
                            State__c : row.long_name
                        });
                        accModel.updateRow(accRow,{
                            Duplicate_State_Name__c : row.short_name
                        });
                    }
                    else if(row.types.includes('country')){
                        //accRow.OtherCountry = row.long_name ;
                        accModel.updateRow(accRow,{
                            clcommon__Country__c : row.long_name
                        });
                    }
                    else if(row.types.includes('street_number')){
                        accModel.updateRow(accRow,{
                            Street_No__c : row.long_name
                        });
                    }
                    else if(row.types.includes('postal_code')){
                        //accRow.OtherPostalCode = row.long_name ;
                        accModel.updateRow(accRow,{
                            clcommon__Zip_Code__c : row.long_name
                        });
                    }
              }) ; 
            }

            //Get and Set the location.
            function geolocate() {
                if (navigator.geolocation) {
                    navigator.geolocation.getCurrentPosition(function(position) {
                      var geolocation = {
                        lat: position.coords.latitude,
                        lng: position.coords.longitude
                      };
                      var circle = new google.maps.Circle(
                          {center: geolocation, radius: position.coords.accuracy});
                      autocomplete7.setBounds(circle.getBounds());
                    });
                }
            }
            function keepCheckingForAutoComplete(){
                if(typeof google === "undefined"){
                    setTimeout(keepCheckingForAutoComplete, 1000);
                }
                else{
                    initAutocompleteTrustTrading();
                }
            }
            keepCheckingForAutoComplete();
            
            
        </script>
</head>

<body>
    <div id="locationField">
        <input id="CompanyTAddress" placeholder="Enter your address" onFocus="geolocate()" type="text" />
    </div>
</body>

<head>
    <script>
        var autocomplete26,
            accModelSMSFShipping = skuid.model.getModel('AccountBillingAddress'),
            accRowSMSFShipping = accModelSMSFShipping.data[0],
            autoCompleteInput26 = document.getElementById('CompanyCAddress');
            //Google Place Initialize
            function initAutocompleteTrustMailing() {
                autocomplete26 = new google.maps.places.Autocomplete(autoCompleteInput26, {types: ['geocode']});
               
                //Restrict the google place only show the specified country address and not allow other country address.
                autocomplete26.setComponentRestrictions({
                   country: ["aus"]
                });
                
                google.maps.event.addListener(autocomplete26, "place_changed", function() {
                  var place = autocomplete26.getPlace();
                  autoCompleteInput26.value = place.formatted_address;
                  if(place){
                    var formatted_address = place.formatted_address;
                    var placeComponent = place.address_components;
                    fillInAddress7(placeComponent,formatted_address);
                  }else{
                    alert('Address not found.Please check your address details.');
                  }
                });
            }
            
            //Address data fillup for each type.
            function fillInAddress7(placeComponent,formatted_address) {
              $.each(placeComponent,function(i,rowSMSFShipping){
                    if(rowSMSFShipping.types=='premise' || rowSMSFShipping.types=='route'){
                        var fullStreetName = rowSMSFShipping.long_name.split(" ");
                        var lengthFullStreetName = fullStreetName.length;
                        if(lengthFullStreetName == 2){
                            accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                            Street_Name__c : rowSMSFShipping.long_name.split(" ")[0]
                            });
                        }
                        else if(lengthFullStreetName > 2){
                            var streetName='';
                            for(var i=0;i<lengthFullStreetName-1;i++){
                                streetName = streetName + rowSMSFShipping.long_name.split(" ")[i]+' ';
                            }
                            accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                                Street_Name__c : streetName
                            });
                        }
                        accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                            Street_Type__c : rowSMSFShipping.long_name.split(" ")[lengthFullStreetName-1]
                        });
                        accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                            Duplicate_Street_Type__c : rowSMSFShipping.short_name.split(" ")[lengthFullStreetName-1]
                        });
                    }
                    else if(rowSMSFShipping.types.includes('sublocality_level_1')){
                        var fullStreetName = rowSMSFShipping.long_name.split(" ");
                        var lengthFullStreetName = fullStreetName.length;
                        if(lengthFullStreetName == 2){
                            accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                                Street_Name__c : rowSMSFShipping.long_name.split(" ")[0]
                            });
                        }
                        else if(lengthFullStreetName > 2){
                            var streetName='';
                            for(var i=0;i<lengthFullStreetName-1;i++){
                                streetName = streetName + rowSMSFShipping.long_name.split(" ")[i]+' ';
                            }
                            accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                                Street_Name__c : streetName
                            });
                        }
                        accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                            Street_Type__c : rowSMSFShipping.long_name.split(" ")[lengthFullStreetName-1]
                        });
                        accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                            Duplicate_Street_Type__c : rowSMSFShipping.short_name.split(" ")[lengthFullStreetName-1]
                        });
                    }
                    else if(rowSMSFShipping.types.includes('locality')){
                            accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                            clcommon__City__c : (rowSMSFShipping.long_name).toUpperCase()
                        });
                    }
                    else if(rowSMSFShipping.types.includes('administrative_area_level_1')){
                        accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                            State__c : rowSMSFShipping.short_name
                        });
                        accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                            Duplicate_State_Name__c : rowSMSFShipping.short_name
                        });
                    }
                    else if(rowSMSFShipping.types.includes('subpremise')){
                            accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                            clcommon__County__c : rowSMSFShipping.long_name
                        });
                    }
                    else if(rowSMSFShipping.types.includes('country')){ 
                           accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                            clcommon__Country__c : rowSMSFShipping.long_name
                        });
                    }
                    else if(rowSMSFShipping.types.includes('street_number')){
                        accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                            Street_No__c : rowSMSFShipping.long_name
                        });
                    }
                    else if(rowSMSFShipping.types.includes('postal_code')){
                            accModelSMSFShipping.updateRow(accRowSMSFShipping,{
                            clcommon__Zip_Code__c : rowSMSFShipping.long_name
                        });
                    }
              }) ; 
            }

            //Get and Set the location.
            function geolocate() {
                if (navigator.geolocation) {
                    navigator.geolocation.getCurrentPosition(function(position) {
                      var geolocation = {
                        lat: position.coords.latitude,
                        lng: position.coords.longitude
                      };
                      var circle = new google.maps.Circle(
                          {center: geolocation, radius: position.coords.accuracy});
                      autocomplete26.setBounds(circle.getBounds());
                    });
                }
            }
            function keepCheckingForAutoComplete(){
                if(typeof google === "undefined"){
                    setTimeout(keepCheckingForAutoComplete, 1000);
                }
                else{
                    initAutocompleteTrustMailing();
                }
            }
            keepCheckingForAutoComplete();
            
        </script>
</head>

<body>
    <div id="locationField">
        <input id="CompanyCAddress" placeholder="Enter your address" onFocus="geolocate()" type="text" />
    </div>
</body>

<html>

<head>
    <script>
        var autocomplete,
            accModel = skuid.model.getModel('SelectedCollateral'),
            accRow = accModel.data[0],
            autoCompleteInput = document.getElementById('CollateralAddress');
            function initAutocomplete() {
                autocomplete = new google.maps.places.Autocomplete(autoCompleteInput, {types: ['geocode']});
                autocomplete.setComponentRestrictions({
                   country: ["aus"]
                });
                
                google.maps.event.addListener(autocomplete, "place_changed", function() {
                  var place = autocomplete.getPlace();
                  autoCompleteInput.value = place.formatted_address;
                  if(place){
                    var formatted_address = place.formatted_address;
                    var placeComponent = place.address_components;
                    fillInAddress(placeComponent,formatted_address);
                  }else{
                    alert('Address not found.Please check your address details.');
                  }
                });
            }
            
            function fillInAddress(placeComponent,formatted_address) {
              $.each(placeComponent,function(i,row){
                    if(row.types=='premise' || row.types=='route'){
                        var fullStreetName = row.long_name.split(" ");
                        var lengthFullStreetName = fullStreetName.length;
                        if(lengthFullStreetName == 2){
                            accModel.updateRow(accRow,{
                            Street_Name__c : row.long_name.split(" ")[0]
                            });
                        }
                        else if(lengthFullStreetName > 2){
                            var streetName='';
                            for(var i=0;i<lengthFullStreetName-1;i++){
                            streetName = streetName + row.long_name.split(" ")[i]+' ';
                            }
                            accModel.updateRow(accRow,{
                                Street_Name__c : streetName
                            });
                        }
                        accModel.updateRow(accRow,{
                            Street_Type__c : row.long_name.split(" ")[lengthFullStreetName-1]
                        });
                        accModel.updateRow(accRow,{
                            Duplicate_Street_Type__c : row.short_name.split(" ")[lengthFullStreetName-1]
                        });
                    }
                    else if(row.types.includes('sublocality_level_1')){
                        var fullStreetName = row.long_name.split(" ");
                        var lengthFullStreetName = fullStreetName.length;
                        if(lengthFullStreetName == 2){
                            accModel.updateRow(accRow,{
                                Street_Name__c : row.long_name.split(" ")[0]
                            });
                        }
                        else if(lengthFullStreetName > 2){
                            var streetName='';
                            for(var i=0;i<lengthFullStreetName-1;i++){
                            streetName = streetName + row.long_name.split(" ")[i]+' ';
                            }
                            accModel.updateRow(accRow,{
                                Street_Name__c : streetName
                            });
                        }
                        accModel.updateRow(accRow,{
                            Street_Type__c : row.long_name.split(" ")[lengthFullStreetName-1]
                        });
                        accModel.updateRow(accRow,{
                            Duplicate_Street_Type__c : row.short_name.split(" ")[lengthFullStreetName-1]
                        });
                    }
                    else if(row.types.includes('locality')){
                        accModel.updateRow(accRow,{
                            clcommon__City__c : (row.long_name).toUpperCase()
                        });
                    }
                    else if(row.types.includes('administrative_area_level_1')){
                        accModel.updateRow(accRow,{
                            clcommon__State__c : row.short_name
                        });
                        accModel.updateRow(accRow,{
                            Duplicate_State_Name__c : row.short_name
                        });
                    }
                    else if(row.types.includes('country')){
                        accModel.updateRow(accRow,{
                            Country__c : row.long_name
                        });
                    }
                    else if(row.types.includes('street_number')){
                        accModel.updateRow(accRow,{
                            Street_No__c : row.long_name
                        });
                    }
                    else if(row.types.includes('postal_code')){
                        accModel.updateRow(accRow,{
                            clcommon__Postal_Code__c : row.long_name
                        });
                    }
                    accModel.updateRow(accRow,{
                        Full_Address__c : formatted_address
                    });

              }) ; 
            }
            function geolocate() {
                if (navigator.geolocation) {
                    navigator.geolocation.getCurrentPosition(function(position) {
                      var geolocation = {
                        lat: position.coords.latitude,
                        lng: position.coords.longitude
                      };
                      var circle = new google.maps.Circle(
                          {center: geolocation, radius: position.coords.accuracy});
                      autocomplete.setBounds(circle.getBounds());
                    });
                }
            }
        </script>
</head>

<body>
    <div id="locationField">
        <input id="CollateralAddress" placeholder="Enter your address" onFocus="geolocate()" type="text" />
    </div>

</body>
